  "description": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"7a3jo\",\"text\":\"Corchea is a paper-based microfluidic system for culture and comunicate bacteria on flow. Its has a hardware that you can make with  a 3D printer and laser cut. The system allows the directed comunications between biofilms and we aim to array biological logic gates on it to make complex information processing.  \",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
